name: [ArtRaccoonee] Fionna the Human
description:
This hypernetwork can generate images in a cartoon, anime, or realistic styles. It's not great, but hey, it works! The original cartoon style can sometimes be tricky.

The hypernetwork is trained on model Any v4.5, but other models, especially in the anime style, are fine too.

Activation tags - FionnaTheHuman, fionna_the_human_girl

For bunny ears don't forget to add - aimal_ears, bunny_ears, animal_hood, bunny_hood, white hood

Also don't forget to play with hypernet strength I prefer somewhere in the 0.6-1

There is room for improvement, and I might do a version 2 if this hypernetwork becomes popular.
